WEBVTT

00:07:58.715 --> 00:08:01.830
So now, give us the internet,
give us Google:

00:08:02.522 --> 00:08:05.252
"I heard that Barack Obama
was born in Kenya.

00:08:05.276 --> 00:08:09.224
Let me Google that -- oh my God!
10 million hits! Look, he was!"

00:08:09.248 --> 00:08:12.388
CA: So this has come as an unpleasant
surprise to a lot of people.

00:08:12.412 --> 00:08:15.260
Social media has often been framed
by techno-optimists

00:08:15.284 --> 00:08:20.531
as this great connecting force
that would bring people together.

00:08:20.555 --> 00:08:24.477
And there have been some
unexpected counter-effects to that.

00:08:24.922 --> 00:08:26.073
JH: That's right.

00:08:26.097 --> 00:08:28.478
That's why I'm very enamored
of yin-yang views

00:08:28.502 --> 00:08:30.120
of human nature and left-right --